PrecisWithdrawal of the entrustment conferred upon the CANADIAN NATIONAL RAILWAY COMPANY in 1979 with respect to two parcels of land situate in the Town of BORDEN, P.E.I., the management, charge and direction of which are to be transferred to the Department of Public Works for the construction of a bridge linking the Provinces of P.E.I. and New Brunswick.
